					<description><![CDATA[<p>Nothing in the world of finance sparks more debate than the &#8220;Old School&#8221; vs &#8220;New School&#8221; fight when it comes to stores of value. On one side is Gold, a</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/gold-vs-btc-showdown-claim-your-share-of-200k/" data-wpel-link="internal">Gold vs BTC Showdown: Claim Your Share of $200K</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Nothing in the world of </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/axoft-raises-55m-to-transform-brain-machine-tech/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">finance </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">sparks more debate than the &#8220;Old School&#8221; vs &#8220;New School&#8221; fight when it comes to stores of value. On one side is Gold, a true-blue, venerable world standard on which we have depended for thousands of years. On the other hand is Bitcoin (BTC), the digital challenger often proclaimed as &#8220;digital gold&#8221; for the new age of the internet. Now, the world&#8217;s leading cryptocurrency exchange, </span><a href="https://www.binance.com/en" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">Binance</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">, is sparking the debate right on the trading floor with the launch of its first campaign, the &#8220;Gold vs BTC Showdown&#8221;.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Initiated on April 22, 2026, traders can select a side to show their confidence by participating in trading volume as well as community growth. The enormous prize pool of up to 200,000 USDC has made the competition more competitive.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">The Battle Lines Are Drawn</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">This is a team competition; you will have to join a team, either Gold or BTC. The goal is to win by trading the mentioned assets to help your team win and to get new users to increase your team&#8217;s ranks.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">If you believe in the proven stability of well-established precious metals, Team Gold will be monitoring the Tether Gold (XAUT) trading pairs, whereas the users betting on a more decentralized financial future shall join Team BTC, the primary partners of Bitcoin pair trading. </span></p>
<div id="attachment_200626" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-200626" class="size-large wp-image-200626" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Gold-vs-BTC-1024x681.jpg" alt="Gold vs BTC" width="1024" height="681" /><p id="caption-attachment-200626" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Unsplash</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">It&#8217;s not about the trading volume that will decide the victor between the two teams, but it is about which team can gather the most &#8220;Eligible New Traders&#8221; who haven&#8217;t traded on Binance Spot and Futures in the past 30 days.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/axoft-raises-55m-to-transform-brain-machine-tech/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">Axoft Raises $55M to Transform Brain-Machine Tech</span></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">How to Claim Your Share</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Joining is easy, but there are a few tasks to complete before receiving any incentives. Traders must navigate to the </span><a href="https://www.binance.com/activity/trading-competition/btcvsgold-vol-1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">event page</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> and hit &#8220;Join Now&#8221; to choose their team. Their team selections cannot be altered after the initial choice, emphasizing the &#8220;all-in&#8221; nature of the competition.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">In order to be eligible for the participant pooling, your aggregated team trading volume must reach at least a $100 USD equivalent in your team-designated pairs. In Team Gold, your team-designated pairs are XAUT/USDT, XAUT/USDC (Spot) and XAUT/USDT (Futures); for Team BTC, it is BTC/USDT, BTC/USDC or BTC/USDT Futures.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">A Scalable Reward System</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Binance has this dynamic prize pool where the pool increases with the growth of the community. Total rewards can vary from an initial 10,000 USDC to a massive 200,000 USDC if new traders are up to 30,000.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The team with the most new traders wins 75% of the entire prize pool, with the other team receiving 25%. In the case of a tie, both teams share equally. Teams are rewarded to be fairly distributed among the traders. For each team, 60% of the rewards are allocated to the new traders, 30% of the rewards go to the referring traders, and 10% of the rewards are distributed to loyal traders who have completed the minimum volume.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/gold-vs-btc-showdown-claim-your-share-of-200k/" data-wpel-link="internal">Gold vs BTC Showdown: Claim Your Share of $200K</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
